{
  "stem": "17301.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 106.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after those people were gone, they said we are-- you are going to be eating breakfast, food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, food consisted of black coffee and nothing else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the black coffee was given to us in-- like a saucepan, a pot for five people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the first one start to drink, and the second one, down to the fifth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If the fifth didn't have enough, I mean, it was just too bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But that-- that was our very first breakfast in-- in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we didn't do too much that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They-- they left us outside [BACKROUND NOISE] most of the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "At lunchtime they came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I saw a lot of people in a very bad shape around me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And for lunchtime, again they gave us a pot with some soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I saw some funny things floating on the top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I had no idea what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But you were so hungry that you didn't care what was in that soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If you were able to just drink a little, because there was nothing to eat in that soup at all, you did it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean you-- we ate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We drank some of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And my mother did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I made sure that my mother had some.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that was our lunch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That was the first day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "For dinner, again, they left us outside most of the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the first day for dinner, they again-- they told us to line up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We lined up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they told us we were going to be fed again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And at that time they gave us a piece of-- piece of bread, a very small piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It looked like pumpernickel to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
